Output demo/orka-chat.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Width 960
Set Height 600
Set FontSize 14
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "orka chat --no-workspace"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "What services are running on this machine and how much disk space is available?"
Enter
Sleep 30s

Type "/quit"
Enter
Sleep 2s
